A Frogeel is a hybrid of a giant frog and a raw cave eel. Players may create frogeels in the Creature Creation basement dungeon under the Tower of Life once they complete the Tower of Life quest.

A frogeel is created by using one pair of giant frog legs and a raw cave eel on the frogeel altar of life found in the western part of the basement. Upon activation of the altar, the Homunculus in the dungeon then creates the monster, which appears near the altar and will attack the player.

Creating and killing a frogeel is required for the It Just Croaked task in the hard Ardougne achievements.
